Cell["\<\
Data with nModes:\[LineSeparator] - fit with nFit = nModes reproduce the \
correct values
- fit with nFit < nModes don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t reproduce
- fit with nFit > nModes reproduce the correct values, but with double \
counting within numerical error

But real data has nModes --> \[Infinity] and also Branch Cut (tail decay) \
contaminating the data. Therefore fit doesn\[CloseCurlyQuote]t work\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.955598444358883*^9, 3.955598566639263*^9}, {
  3.955598635463355*^9, 
